strings.Value: "I don't care about his motives. Snot-nosed Tristian betrayed us. I'll never forget it."
"Your anger is fully justified. A traitor can have no forgiveness."
"It's no surprise his vaunted principles were meaningless even to him."

"Pffft! Betrayed, schmetrayed... our kind betrays each other three times before dinner!"
"It's no wonder he betrayed us. What's surprising is that we trusted him in the first place!"
